{"tid":1895434,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Mina疑似中咗武漢肺炎???","createTime":"2020-02-24T14:03:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T08:04:59.000Z","uid":193951,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"21768f6444e29877ddee6c6eb439b63744a5e240","tid":1895434,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T14:03:07.000Z","msg":"韓國新冠病毒疫情延燒，人心惶惶，JTBC電視臺氣象女主播金敏娥（김민아），昨（23日）在主持《英雄聯盟》LCK職業聯賽賽後訪問時發燒，立刻被送醫接受新冠病毒檢測，她參與錄製的節目緊急停播，節目相關同仁也全部自我隔離。<br />\n<br />\n據韓聯社報導，因應新冠肺炎疫情，《英雄聯盟》LCK職業聯賽雖然正常進行，但不開放觀眾入場觀賽，賽事官方也對疫情採取高度警戒。然而昨賽事現場突發意外，負責現場主持、採訪的甜美女主播金敏娥發燒了。<br />\n<br />\nJTBC電視臺表示，為以防萬一，金敏娥參與的《早間&amp;》節目組的全部成員，目前也都自我隔離。據瞭解，金敏娥是否確診，結果將於24日下午揭曉。<br />\n<br />\n金敏娥自我隔離後，在IG上發文表示，很抱歉讓大家擔心，但她的症狀並不嚴重，確診（新冠肺炎）的可能性也很小。不過立刻離開錄影現場是一個最好的選擇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c1b02890cc45d24e9e2459ce1f1a23f9dcea9fc","tid":1895434,"uid":190258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T14:04:39.000Z","msg":"韓妺係無辜的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e82781d2dad2516f2a6ba5de6e749bb853ca002","tid":1895434,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T14:07:43.000Z","msg":"岩岩仲諗住改佢個名做USER NAME<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f693ac75dd16a39a749682fd570689b054efed8c","tid":1895434,"uid":117802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T14:12:44.000Z","msg":"又係LOL害人不淺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快啲摺咗隻game啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b502cec262daa2da88699386d868d27d0df795ea","tid":1895434,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T14:13:08.000Z","msg